  cgA-1m   166    166.37  3.44     748.95   1298.29  977.27   1233.13  1300.23  1300.23
  cgB-4k   5      0.02    0.02     181.74   761.32   742.39   759.17   759.17   759.17

  cgA-1m   167    166.51  1.98     748.68   1549.41  809.50   1451.23  1551.89  1551.89
